		<RichText x="1410" y="255" width="424" height="114" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">曼陀草原地蓄力，孢囊发光，而后迅速进行多次弹射，接触造成<span color="#99ff85">55%,16.5%,<br/>5.5%</span><span>伤害；接着重重坠地，造成</span><span color="#99ff85">100%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="255" width="431" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">曼陀草进行1-3次的跳跃攻击，造成<span color="#99ff85">50%,20%</span><span>伤害，「脆性」状态会经常施放失败，表现为突然的倒地。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="543" width="439" height="114" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">距离较远时，曼陀草向前方发射6枚曲轨孢弹，造成<span color="#99ff85">40%,20%,7.2%</span><span>伤害，会重复施放2-3次；「脆性」状态下只发射3枚孢弹，且只连续施放一次。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="543" width="424" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">曼陀草开始倒立并朝玩家方向旋转，移动一小段距离，接触造成<span color="#99ff85">50%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="1119" width="424" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">距离较远时，孢子抛射一枚草球，造成<span color="#99ff85">80%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="799" width="1017" height="114" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">曼陀草初始处于「刚性」聚合状态，首次<span textDecoration="underline">分裂倒计时</span><span>为</span><span color="#ffdfbf">35s</span><span>，后续为</span><span color="#ffdfbf">38s</span><span>；倒计时结束后，在9-12m范围内分裂为10个</span><span textDecoration="underline">孢子</span><span>，持续17s；之后恢复。若期间击败8个及以上孢子，则会使曼陀草恢复后退出「刚性」状态，进入「脆性」聚合状态，并使分裂倒计时延长至</span><span color="#ffdfbf">44s</span><span>。<br/>低于</span><span color="#ffebbf">20%生命值</span><span>则根据剩余生命分裂对应数量的孢子(2%/个)；低于</span><span color="#ffebbf">2%生命值</span><span>则不再分裂。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="1119" width="349" height="28" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">孢子轻轻撞击，造成<span color="#99ff85">100%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="66" y="1167" width="435" height="97" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.7490196078431373">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="16" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">孢子：生命值为曼陀草的<span color="#ffdfbf">10%</span><span>，攻击力为</span><span color="#ffdfbf">18275</span><span>(7.0B2 Lv.103)或为</span><span color="#ffdfbf">6894</span><span>(2.8B2 Lv.100 历经百战)，重/韧为45/50<br/>每击败一只扣除曼陀草</span><span color="#ffdfbf">2%生命值</span><span>。<br/>分裂倒计时：可被</span><span color="#ffacff">雷</span><span>与</span><span color="#ff9999">火</span><span>元素攻击加速，根据其元素量扣除</span><span color="#ffdfbf">n*1s</span><span>或</span><span color="#ffdfbf">0.15s</span><span>。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
