				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="16" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">孢子分裂范围：中心范围<span color="#ffdfbf">0-0.3m</span><span>，1个孢子；内层范围</span><span color="#ffdfbf">2-4.5m</span><span>，3个孢子；中层范围</span><span color="#ffdfbf">5-8m</span><span>，3个孢子；外层范围</span><span color="#ffdfbf">9-12m</span><span>，3个孢子。<br/>处于「刚性」聚合状态时，抗打断0.12。</span></p>
